  "response": "I can\u2019t browse the internet to find specific items for sale, but I can help you with some general tips on where to look for t-shirts. Popular online retailers include:\n\n1. **Amazon** - A wide variety of t-shirts are available.\n2. **Etsy** - Great for unique or custom designs.\n3. **Redbubble** - Features designs by independent artists.\n4. **Zazzle** - Customizable t-shirts available.\n5. **eBay** - You might find new or used options here.\n6. **Local stores** - Check department stores, clothing outlets, or specialty shops nearby.\n\nIf you have a specific design or brand in mind, let me know, and I can provide more tailored suggestions!",
